@@ -49,0 +49,7 @@
+# Canonicalize for riscv which autoconf-config.sub doesn't handle
+if echo $* | grep '^riscv\(32\|64\)-linux' >/dev/null ; then
+    result=`echo $@ | sed 's/linux/unknown-linux/'`
+    echo $result
+    exit
+fi
